data.description: Location, Location! This property in paradise is on the quiet end of a county road, with uninterrupted views of the sunset over the coast range and is minutes to downtown Eugene.  The neighbors raise horses, livestock, blue berries and hay and you could do the same.  All just minutes from the towns of Eugene, Junction City as well as  Fern Ridge Lake and the Eugene Airport.  The home is full of light with walls of windows, extra tall ceilings, large primary suite, bonus room upstairs is counted as bedroom has ½ bath with room for full bath.  This fully fenced property includes a 50X20 Rv Garage, 25x25 2 stall barn, 44x22 3-car garage, 22x16 1-car garage 14x10 Workshop, Water Fall /pond, fenced pasture in back is serene and private.  An oversized garage was professionally converted could be family/game room, mother in law suite (with no steps) etc, you decide how to enjoy this oversized space.  Schedule your showing today.
